data.description: MOVE-IN READY WALLKILL HOME - Nestled back on a wooded lot surrounded by mature trees and old stack stoned walls is this beautiful Raised Ranch home. On your main level you have a large kitchen with granite countertops, island with seating, new stainless-steel appliances, a large dining area open to the kitchen, nice-sized living room and hardwood floors thru-out. There are three bedrooms including your primary bedroom with double closets and ensuite and walk-in shower, two more generously sized bedrooms and bathroom with tub/shower combination. Downstairs is a family room with hardwood flooring, recessed lighting, surround sound and a large laundry room with washer/dryer. Family room walks out to a paver patio that opens up into a private rear yard with a shed. This home is on a lovely dead-end cul-de-sac and is close to local area wineries, farmstands, Minnewaska State Park, Gardiner Skydive Ranch and more area attractions. Fabulous commuter location only 7.3 miles to the Newburgh/Beacon Bridge for easy access to the Metro North train station into NYC. A truly lovely home!
